description:
On today’s Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to the MMQB’s Albert Breer about last night’s game and where he thinks OBJ may land. Dean Blandino discusses the controversial taunting call. Grant Hill tells stories about Coach K as well as how much he thinks he would have made at Duke with the NIL
